@namespace PgmStudio.Client.Pages.AuthoringParts

<section class="ds-section" id="review">
  <div class="ds-section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-kicker">05</p>
      <h2>Review &amp; Export</h2>
    </div>
    <p>A generated map can be structurally valid yet <em>unplayable</em>. Traversability is the closing
       gate — a disconnected spawn–wool chain blocks export with HTTP&nbsp;409.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ds-subsection">
    <h3>All checks pass — export enabled</h3>
    <article class="ds-example">
      <div class="ds-example-label">Pre-flight checks · Export XML live</div>
      <div class="ds-panel-frame">
        <div class="workspace-scroll">
          <section class="panel-section">
            <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
              <h2 class="section-title">Pre-flight checks</h2>
              <span class="badge badge--success">Ready</span>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Round-trip</span><span class="step-detail">349 / 349 codec parity — no field lost in XML ↔ dict</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Mirror check</span><span class="step-detail">DeriveFacets(generate(intent)) recovered the intent — generator and categorizer are inverses</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Buildability</span><span class="step-detail">All spawn / wool / monument placements on solid ground</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Traversability</span><span class="step-detail">spawn ↔ wool chain connected — all 4 teams reachable across the build geometry</span></div>

              <div class="console-wrap">
                <div class="console-header">
                  <span class="console-title">Generate &amp; validate log</span>
                  <button class="console-clear-btn" disabled>Clear</button>
                </div>
                <div class="console-output">
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.001] intent → generate: 4 teams · 4 spawns · 4 wools · 49 regions · 35 filters · 16 apply-rules</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.004] codec round-trip: 349/349 fields match</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.008] mirror check: spawn/protection ✓ wool/room ✓ build ✓ wool/monument ✓</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.011] buildability: 4/4 spawns on surface · 4/4 wool rooms on buildable ground</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--success">[00:00.019] traversability: connected — blue↔green↔red↔yellow chain verified</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--success">[00:00.020] export gate OPEN — GET /map/thunder_blank/xml → 200</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-footer">
              <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary"><i data-lucide="download"></i> Export XML</button>
              <span class="panel-save-status">thunder_blank · proto 1.5.0</span>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ds-subsection">
    <h3>Traversability fails — export blocked (the HTTP 409 gate)</h3>
    <article class="ds-example">
      <div class="ds-example-label">Pre-flight checks · Export XML disabled</div>
      <div class="ds-panel-frame">
        <div class="workspace-scroll">
          <section class="panel-section">
            <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
              <h2 class="section-title">Pre-flight checks</h2>
              <span class="badge badge--error">Blocked</span>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Round-trip</span><span class="step-detail">349 / 349 codec parity</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Mirror check</span><span class="step-detail">intent recovered from generated structure</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--done"></span><span class="step-label">Buildability</span><span class="step-detail">placements valid</span></div>
              <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot step-dot--error"></span><span class="step-label">Traversability</span><span class="step-detail">Yellow island not reachable — add a bridge in Build</span></div>

              <div class="panel-warning">
                <strong>Export blocked.</strong> Yellow team cannot reach the wool rooms and cannot be reached by
                attackers — the spawn–wool chain is not connected. Return to the <strong>Build</strong> step and add a
                bridge across the gap between <code>yellow-main-and-spawn</code> and the centre island. Traversability
                re-runs automatically when you come back.
              </div>

              <div class="console-wrap">
                <div class="console-header">
                  <span class="console-title">Generate &amp; validate log</span>
                  <button class="console-clear-btn" disabled>Clear</button>
                </div>
                <div class="console-output">
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.004] codec round-trip: 349/349 fields match</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--info">[00:00.011] buildability: placements valid</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--error">[00:00.031] traversability: NOT CONNECTED</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--error">[00:00.031]   isolated: yellow-spawn (16,-93) · yellow-wool (-7,-112)</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--error">[00:00.031]   GET /map/thunder_blank/xml → HTTP 409: spawn-wool chain not connected</div>
                  <div class="console-line console-line--warning">[00:00.032] fix: add a bridge between yellow-main-and-spawn and center-island</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-footer">
              <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary" disabled><i data-lucide="download"></i> Export XML</button>
              <span class="panel-save-status">HTTP 409 — traversability gate</span>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
